          <li>Completed tasks now moved down the list</li>
          <li>Toggle for each list for hiding / showing completed tasks</li>
          <li>Added Tags bar under task text. If task have tags, they will be visible.</li>
          <li>Added priority flags</li>
          <li>Added setting for selecting new task position</li>
          <li>Sidebar redesign</li>
          <li>Using GNOME 46 platform with latest libadwaita widgets</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
